No. 24,

Misc.

Gullahorn et al. v. United States. Petitioners pro se. Solicitor General Rankin, Assistant Attorney General Olney, Beatrice Rosenberg and Felicia Dubrovsky for the United States.

Motion of Robert Clyde Sanders to withdraw from the petition for writ of certiorari granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit and for other relief denied.
